description:
Comment: 11 pages, 5 figures; In the revised version, v is renormalized;
  Kinetic eqs/expressions are modified/rectified; Some figures are redrawn. To
  appear in Phys. Plasmas (2014)

  Polynome codes and code evaluation; arithmetical theory frames;
$\mu$-recursive race for decision; decision correctness; decision termination;
correct termination in theory $T = PR$ of Primitive Recursion; comparison with
the negative result of Matiyasevich; positive solution in p.r.
non-infinite-descent theory $\pi R=PR+(\pi).$
